话术将直播间的用户引导至另一个无资质认证且只有 2.1 万粉丝的普通账号。该账号头像为白底红字「点开」图片，昵称为「高然先生官方助理」，助理通过该账号私信功能与用户一对一沟通。因为新黄河记者没有及时回复对方私信，则收到对方一次又一次的语音通话邀请。网红医生「伪科普」背后的流量生意：跨科擦边，发暗广推销药 _ 上观新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665871845"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItfbboLPJgVcQAxoJMTEwMjQ5MzM1ILrOzrYGMAA4lQFAE3IJNjY1ODcxODQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1725225518.664177", "card_id": "Q_661957618", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "炮兵到底有多少技术含量?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "都说炮兵是技术兵种，技术含量到底有多少？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8bc1f041057e00fafab4f2e5e9f64cba_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661957618"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItfbboLPJgVcQAxoJMTA5Mzc5NTExIKOT5LQGMAA4wQFAFHIJNjYxOTU3NjE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1725225518.664414", "card_id": "Q_665720532", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "郑钦文能拿下 2024 美国网球公开赛的冠军吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "北京时间 29 日凌晨，2024 美国网球公开赛展开女单第二轮争夺，奥运会女单冠军、赛会 7 号种子郑钦文逆转取胜，成功闯入美网 32 强。 这位世界排名第七、巴黎奥运会网球冠军能否取得 2024 年美国网球公开赛冠军？能否再续写辉煌？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e10ccfea2b7f30f8d00c31c61b6a28b1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665720532"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItfbboLPJgVcQAxoJMTEwMjE1NDQ2I